verses.text:
She is weary with toil;
yet her great rust,
rust by fire, doesn’t leave her.

‘Speak to the house of Israel, “The Lord GOD says: ‘Behold, I will
profane my sanctuary, the pride of your power, the desire of your eyes, and that which your soul pities;
and your sons and your daughters whom you have left behind will fall by the sword.
